videos.description: 1H (9:42) ORE G Payton Pritchard runs free in transition lofts it to F Chris Boucher who slams it home.
videos.headline: Pritchard and Boucher connect for the alley-oop
Dillon Brooks draws contact on atheltic finish around the rim

videos.description: 2H (15:46) ORE Chris Boucher made Dunk. Assisted by Dillon Brooks.
videos.headline: Ducks' Brooks makes pretty assist along baseline, Boucher slams it home
Kavell Bigby-Williams spikes away the Tiger shot attempt.
